Package: evictionAddresses
Title: A Data Entry Dashboard, API, and Reporting Tool for Eviction Addresses
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Brancen", "Gregory", ,
      "bgregory@okpolicy.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Eviction case documents contain addresses and are public records,
    but they are not available in a format that is easy to use.
    This package provides a dashboard for data entry, an API for accessing the
    data, and a reporting tool for analyzing the data.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
